<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>RATIONS - Supply Depot</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Courier+Prime:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400;1,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Georgia, serif;
            background: #d4c19e;
            color: #2d2d1f;
            line-height: 1.6;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        /* Navigation */
        .nav-container {
            background: rgba(74, 93, 58, 0.9);
            border-bottom: 3px solid #4a5d3a;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .nav-content {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
        }

        .logo {
            font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #d4c19e;
            text-decoration: none;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 0;
            list-style: none;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            color: #d4c19e;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover,
        .nav-links a.active {
            background: #8FBC8F;
            color: #2d2d1f;
            border-color: #4a5d3a;
        }

        /* Document Container */
        .document-container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            padding: 0 2rem;
        }

        /* Classification Header */
        .classified-header {
            background: #4a5d3a;
            color: #d4c19e;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0.5rem;
            font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        /* Document Page */
        .document-page {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
            border: 3px solid #8a7a5a;
            padding: 3rem;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .document-page::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            left: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            bottom: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #8a7a5a;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        /* Document Stamps */
        .document-stamps {
            position: absolute;
            top: 2rem;
            right: 2rem;
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .stamp {
            background: #ff6b6b;
            color: white;
            padding: 4px 8px;
            font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            transform: rotate(15deg);
            border: 2px solid #cc0000;
        }

        .stamp-2 {
            transform: rotate(-10deg);
            background: #4a5d3a;
            border-color: #2d3d1f;
        }

        .stamp-3 {
            transform: rotate(8deg);
            background: #8FBC8F;
            color: #2d2d1f;
            border-color: #6b8a4a;
        }

        /* Page Header */
        .page-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #4a5d3a;
            padding-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .doc-title {
            font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #4a5d3a;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .doc-subtitle {
            font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
            color: #6b7a5b;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* Document Info */
        .doc-info {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .info-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 0.5rem;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            border: 1px solid #8a7a5a;
        }

        .info-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4a5d3a;
        }

        /* Sections */
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .section-header {
            background: rgba(74, 93, 58, 0.8);
            color: #d4c19e;
            padding: 1rem;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            border-left: 5px solid #8FBC8F;
        }

        .section-content {
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #2d2d1f;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .section-content p {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        /* Product Specifications */
        .product-specs {
            background: rgba(143, 188, 143, 0.2);
            border: 2px solid #8FBC8F;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }

        .specs-header {
            font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #4a5d3a;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .specs-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
            font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
        }

        .spec-item {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
            border: 1px solid #8a7a5a;
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .spec-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4a5d3a;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
        }

        .spec-value {
            color: #2d2d1f;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        /* Order Information */
        .order-info {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
            border: 2px solid #8a7a5a;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .price-display {
            font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ff6b6b;
            margin: 1rem 0;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .order-button {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8FBC8F 0%, #6b8a4a 100%);
            color: #2d2d1f;
            border: 2px solid #4a5d3a;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .order-button:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #9ACD32 0%, #7ba428 100%);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        /* Footer */
        .document-footer {
            background: #2d2d1f;
            color: #8a7a5a;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
            font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav-content {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 1rem;
                padding: 1rem;
            }

            .nav-links {
                gap: 1rem;
            }

            .document-container {
                padding: 0 1rem;
            }

            .document-page {
                padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
            }

            .doc-title {
                font-size: 2rem;
                letter-spacing: 3px;
            }

            .doc-info {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .specs-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="nav-container">
        <div class="nav-content">
            <a href="/" class="logo">RATIONS</a>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="/supply-depot" class="active">Supply Depot</a></li>
                <li><a href="/mission-brief">Mission Brief</a></li>
                <li><a href="/merchandise">Merchandise</a></li>
                <li><a href="/field-manual">Field Manual</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="document-container">
        <!-- Classification Header -->
        <div class="classified-header">
            UNCLASSIFIED - AUTHORIZED FOR PUBLIC DISTRIBUTION
        </div>

        <!-- Supply Depot Document -->
        <div class="document-page">
            <div class="document-stamps">
                <div class="stamp stamp-1">APPROVED</div>
                <div class="stamp stamp-2">AVAILABLE</div>
                <div class="stamp stamp-3">STOCKED</div>
            </div>

            <div class="page-header">
                <h1 class="doc-title">SUPPLY DEPOT</h1>
                <p class="doc-subtitle">STANDARD ISSUE TACTICAL SEASONING</p>
            </div>

            <div class="doc-info">
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">ITEM CLASS:</div>
                    <div>CULINARY ENHANCEMENT</div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">AVAILABILITY:</div>
                    <div>IN STOCK</div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">PROCUREMENT:</div>
                    <div>IMMEDIATE</div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">CLEARANCE:</div>
                    <div>CIVILIAN AUTHORIZED</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Product Description -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-header">I. PRODUCT OVERVIEW</div>
                <div class="section-content">
                    <p>The STANDARD ISSUE Tactical Seasoning represents decades of military culinary research and field testing. Originally developed for armed forces operating in challenging environments where flavor superiority was essential for morale maintenance.</p>
                    
                    <p>Following extensive declassification reviews, this formerly restricted seasoning compound has been approved for civilian procurement. Each container provides sufficient seasoning for approximately 100 standard meal preparations.</p>
                    
                    <p>Quality assurance protocols ensure consistent flavor deployment across all production batches. No artificial additives or preservatives compromise the tactical effectiveness of this seasoning system.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Specifications -->
            <div class="product-specs">
                <div class="specs-header">TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS</div>
                <div class="specs-grid">
                    <div class="spec-item">
                        <div class="spec-label">CONTENT WEIGHT:</div>
                        <div class="spec-value">4.5 OZ (128g)</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="spec-item">
                        <div class="spec-label">CONTAINER TYPE:</div>
                        <div class="spec-value">TACTICAL SHAKER</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="spec-item">
                        <div class="spec-label">SHELF LIFE:</div>
                        <div class="spec-value">24 MONTHS</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="spec-item">
                        <div class="spec-label">STORAGE TEMP:</div>
                        <div class="spec-value">ROOM TEMPERATURE</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="spec-item">
                        <div class="spec-label">SODIUM CONTENT:</div>
                        <div class="spec-value">BALANCED</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="spec-item">
                        <div class="spec-label">ALLERGEN STATUS:</div>
                        <div class="spec-value">NONE DETECTED</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Deployment Instructions -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-header">II. DEPLOYMENT INSTRUCTIONS</div>
                <div class="section-content">
                    <p><strong>BASIC DEPLOYMENT:</strong> Apply directly to target food items during or after cooking process. Recommended deployment rate: 1/4 teaspoon per standard protein serving.</p>
                    
                    <p><strong>ADVANCED APPLICATIONS:</strong> Refer to Field Manual FM-RATIONS-001 for comprehensive tactical deployment procedures, including specialized techniques for various food categories and operational environments.</p>
                    
                    <p><strong>STORAGE PROTOCOLS:</strong> Maintain container seal integrity between deployments. Store in cool, dry environment away from direct sunlight to preserve tactical effectiveness.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Order Information -->
            <div class="order-info">
                <h3 style="color: #4a5d3a; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace; letter-spacing: 2px;">PROCUREMENT DETAILS</h3>
                <div class="price-display">$14.95</div>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #2d2d1f;">Includes standard shipping to continental United States. International deployment available upon request.</p>
                <button class="order-button">INITIATE PROCUREMENT</button>
                <p style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #6b7a5b;">30-day satisfaction guarantee. Quality assured or full refund authorized.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Footer Classification -->
            <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 3rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 2px solid #8a7a5a;">
                <p style="color: #4a5d3a; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1rem; font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;">
                    CLASSIFICATION: UNCLASSIFIED<br>
                    DISTRIBUTION: UNLIMITED<br>
                    DOCUMENT ID: SD-RATIONS-001
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="document-footer">
        <p>RATIONS COMMAND - TACTICAL CULINARY DIVISION</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.8rem; opacity: 0.7;">All products manufactured to military specifications</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>